originalText.text:
Positive from the first minute onwards. Very dedicated professional with lots of empathy, understanding, compassion, practical takes, very much involved and sincere.
And a long history of treating lots of different situations, lifestyles, ages and circumstances. A most valuable asset. No new kid on the block. Filled with wisdom.
Can't say enough about what a fine therapist Dr. Black is.
